\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0495452453133421e-22, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany and Australia, the two outfits behind the CONCACAF powerhouse, need to win and overcome a significant goal difference in order to move into the quarterfinals as a group winner.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 486, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2750654582916362e-16, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 498, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.64183707143065e-40, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CONCACAF\", \"score\": 0.9999999992010089, \"rank\": 7.990560027102978e-10, \"text\": \"CONCACAF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CONCACAF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CONCACAF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The front three, otherwise known as \\\"The Triple Threat\\\", has completely shut down the narrative many were pushing ahead of this competition \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 are the USWNT clinical enough in the final third?\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 824, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mallory Swanson, Sophia Smith, and Trinity Rodman have scored or assisted on all seven of the United States' goals so far at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"score\": 0.7999394196426524, \"rank\": 0.24902275248585262, \"text\": \"Mallory\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\"}, {\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swanson\", \"score\": 0.9999999769988792, \"rank\": 1.3526080522740557e-08, \"text\": \"Swanson\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swanson\"}, {\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_of_Hanover\", \"score\": 0.8147052707038189, \"rank\": 0.22743772752189426, \"text\": \"Sophia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_of_Hanover\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_of_Hanover\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trinity Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\"